Text: Renew job is great so far I am starting to get busy which is good but I am a little overwhelmed I really think I am going to like this rotation The hours are good so far I get in at around AM and leave around PM Pretty normal I have been relaxing a lot at night I am trying to save some money so I am not going out as much I have also been swimming at the YMCA on Tuesdays and Thursdays Thats all thats new over here Stay warm on your motorcycle Chris CT PM To Alicia ES cc Subject Re Oh now youre teasing me I went riding last night I think I need some winter motorcycle gear My brother and I are taking a biking trip in November dont know where we are going yet Hows the new job What do you do with yourself in the evenings now Alicia ES PM To Chris CT cc Subject Long time no talk How have you been Have you been riding your motorcycle a lot Maybe we can go to Barnabys next week
